ActAppropriation Act No. 1, 2017-18
PrecisAppointment of Stephen de Boer as Ambassador and Permanent Representative of Canada to the World Trade Organization, in Geneva; André Frenette as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Haiti; Shauna Hemingway as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Dominican Republic; Marcel Lebleu as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Colombia; Patricia Peña as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Chile; Caterina Ventura as High Commissioner for Canada in Brunei Darussalam; and Louis Verret as Ambassador Extraordinary and Plenipotentiary of Canada to the Republic of Mali.
